snippet.title: Eldritch Exterminators - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Eldritch Exterminators ➤ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2493910/Eldritch_Exterminators/

Discord ➤ https://discord.gg/QvJMb2G

Face the Eldritch hordes. You are a possessed gun, feeding on the souls of the dead. Grow your power and challenge the Eldritch Gods for Dominion over the Void. Slay the Forgotten Ones and harness Unspeakables in this Bullet Heaven, and escape the ties that bind.
